This complete collection of luxury makeup brushes includes the essential brushes used by professional makeup artists throughout the makeup world. How to clean makeup brushes: 1. Run the bristles of brush under warm running water. 2. Apply a small amount of gentle shampoo to bristles and work into a light lather. 3. Rinse bristles thoroughly under running water.
